<div id="legal">

    <h1>Terms of Services</h1>

    <p>
        You as a user are allowed to connect an account through other services such as Discord and Github.
        This account can be used to upload content to active events and vote on entries of active events. 
        By using VoteMyst you will abide to the Terms of Services of any of the possible authorization services.
    </p>

    <p>You can read more about their Terms of Services here:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://discordapp.com/terms">Discord Terms Of Service</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://help.github.com/en/github/site-policy/github-terms-of-service">Github Terms Of Service</a></li>
